  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  text: 'The Player Prefab includes the Animal Controller, a Brain camera and all
    the virtual cameras that each player will use.


    - All References are set
    directly in the Animal Controller (Do not use Scritptable Variables)


    Aim
    -> Camera  = Brain Camera

    Animal Controller.MainCamera = Brain Camera


    Third
    Person Follow.Brain = Brain Camera

    Third Person Follow.Target = Animal -
    Internal Components - Main Camera Target'
